<h3 class="md:text-lg">How would our Special Operations Forces perform in North Korea?</h3>
<div class="category-date flex justify-between md:hidden">
<span class="category text-xxs uppercase"></span>
<span class="date text-xxs uppercase">Apr 12</span>
</div>
</div>
</span>
 </a>
</div>
<div class="news-box md:px-2 md:w-1/3">
